      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-10 min or until the sauce has thickened to a bolognese sauce-like consistency – this is your<strong> lentil ragù</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
