    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>courgette</strong> to the<strong> </strong>lentil ragù and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the starchy pasta water if it's looking a little dry!</p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> Tuscan-style lentil & roasted courgette ragù</strong></p>",
